<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <title>North Canton Church</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "bootstrap", "application" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <script type="text/javascripts">
    <% if Rails.env.production? -%>
      var _gaq = _gaq || [];
      _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-28608739-1']);
      _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);

      (function() {
      var ga = document.createElement('script'); ga.type = 'text/javascript'; ga.async = true;
      ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' : 'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';
      var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);
      })();
    <% end -%>
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-wrap container">
      <div id="header-inner">
        <h1><a href="/" id="logo"><img src="images/logo.png" width="328" height="82" alt="Hope Christian Fellowship"></a></h1>
        <div id="tagline">"Revealing Jesus through building relationships"</div>
        <div id="menu">
          <%= content_tag :ul do %>
            <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
            <li><a href="mission.html">MISSION</a></li>
            <li><a href="about.html">ABOUT</a></li>
            <li><a href="events.html">EVENTS</a></li>
            <li><a hre/f="contact.html">CONTACT</a></li>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%= content_tag :div, :class => 'carousel' do %>
        <%= content_tag :div, :class => 'carousel-inner' do %>

          <%= content_tag :div, :class => "item active" do %>
            <%= image_tag 'october_morning.jpg' %>
            <%= content_tag :div, :class => 'carousel-caption' do %>
            <p><strong>GET INVOLVED!</strong><br>
              Joining us here at Hope Christian Fellowship is not difficult. 
              We would love to have you! Yet, we understand that you may need 
              to take time to pray about your commitment. 
              <a href="#">Click Here to find out more</a>.
            </p>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>

          <%= content_tag :div, :class => "item" do %>
            <%= image_tag 'refreshing.jpg' %>
            <%= content_tag :div, :class => 'carousel-caption' do %>
            <p><strong>TIMES OF REFRESHING: PRAYER AND WORSHIP</strong><br> Join us for a time of prayer, worship and fellowship. Monday February 6th at 7:00PM <a href="#">Click Here to find out more</a>.</p>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>

          <%= content_tag :div, :class => "item" do %>
            <%= image_tag 'ocean.jpg' %>
            <%= content_tag :div, :class => 'carousel-caption' do %>
            <p><strong>BREAKTHROUGH PRAYER: HOME GROUP</strong><br>You can order the book "Breakthrough Prayer" by Jim Cymbala, but you not need to book to be a part of the home group. <br><a href="#">Click Here to find out more</a>.</p>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to "&lsaquo;".html_safe, '', :class => 'carousel-control left', 'data-slide' => "prev" %>
        <%= link_to "&rsaquo;".html_safe, '', :class => 'carousel-control right', 'data-slide' => "next" %>
      <% end %>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class='span6'>
          <h3>HCF NORTH CANTON WELCOMES <em>YOU!</em></h3>
          <hr>
          <p>Here at Hope Christian Fellowship we believe that every person is   important to God.  He has a plan for each of our lives.  He desires us   to experience love, acceptance and forgiveness in His church, the Body   of Christ.</p>
          <p>We invite you to join us as we enjoy the presence of God, not only in   our scheduled gatherings and activities, but also in the lives of one   another. </p>
        </div>
        <div class='span3'>
         <h3>SERVICE TIMES</h3>
         <hr>
         <p><strong>North Canton</strong><br>
           Sunday, 10:00 A.M.</p>
         <p><strong>Lisbon</strong><br>
           Early Service<br>
           Sunday, 9:00 A.M.<br>
           Late Service<br>
           Sunday, 10:45 A.M.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='span3'>
          <h3>LOCATIONS</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>
            <strong>North Canton</strong><br>
            Hope Christian Fellowship North Canton<br>
            116 7th St<br>
            North Canton, OH 44720<br>
            330-433-1061
          </p>
          <p><strong>Lisbon</strong><br>
            Hope Christian Fellowship<br>
            13320 St Rt 7<br>
            Lisbon, OH 44432<br>
            330-385-4673 (330-385-HOPE)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='footer row-fluid'>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Follow Us on Facebook!</h3>
          <hr>&nbsp;</hr>
          <p><a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100002867512169"><img src="images/fb-icon.png" alt="Follow Hope North Canton on Facebook" width="50" height="50" align="left" style="padding-right:15px"></a><strong><em><a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100002867512169" target="_blank">Like Us!</a></em></strong><br>
          Become a friend of Hope North Canton! Get the latest updates, photos, and share with us!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Giving to HCCF</h3>
          <hr>&nbsp;</hr>
          <p>In addition to your normal tithe. We will be taking an additional offering for the Pregnancy Support Center (PSC). Please us a seperate envelope for this offering and mark it for PSC...</p>
          <p><strong><a href="donate.html">Read More</a></strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Prayer of the Month</h3>
          <hr>&nbsp;</hr>
          <p>Dear Lord God: I thank you for my church, for those who worship next to me each Sunday. Thank you for giving me these loving souls to walk alongside me on my journey...</p>
          <p><strong><a href="prayer.html">Read More</a></strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row-fluid" id="copyright">
        <div class='span12'> 
          <hr>
        </div>
        <div class='span6'>
          &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Hope Christian Fellowship North Canton
        </div>
        <div class='span4 offset4'>
          <address>116 7th St. North Canton, OH 44720 330-433-1061</address>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
